{"tid":1626751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【今晚九點大行動】唔好等到聽日遊行，有急事要今晚即做！","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:52:42.000Z","uid":238693,"like":204,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d10f1e6136e6f84c7ef96ff4a052adfb48f5bc30","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"點解呢兩晚popo咁被動？死城一日就係想大家怯，淺黃街坊懷疑自己，停港鐵焗住留喺屋企。<br />\n<br />\n我哋呢刻最緊要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">壯膽</span>，商場封撚晒唔代表冇得大合唱，我哋要回歸主場：屋企！<br />\n最近大家少咗九點十點鳩叫，今晚九點就要叫足唱足一個鐘！<br />\n等勇武屋企休養時更快回血，和理非唔駛戴口罩都可以做嘢，未到十一點<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完全合法</span>！<br />\n屋企都唔敢叫，聽日點會有三百萬人上街啊？大家盡share 盡做！<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港，聽日見！"},{"pid":"b769ebc1c7107037d84ff69701e893a8ee16050f","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"推到九點"},{"pid":"06bc4123979e40334c8f80f75b67e542b39d51b4","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"推到九點"},{"pid":"c136306a5130698a54259f25873e4052f7b85184","tid":1626751,"uid":93451,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果學校範圍唔算公眾地方 <br />\n聽日一齊返學校有無得諗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都認為聽日係和理非回合[url][/url]<br />\n想出去表達 打下條國際線<br />\n但揾唔到一個一開始同最後唔比人清場嘅方法<br />\n但如果我地帶口罩係大學<br />\n校友\b,大學生,中學生 仲有唔同年齡愛香港嘅香港人<br />\n一齊進行學術討論討論下香港又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹諗到想討論下可行性<br />\n可能時間係好趕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但聽日最緊要係做到野 同安全</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地好耐無新嘅創意啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果八大有好多香港人坐晒係到<br />\n帶口罩表達自己意見<br />\n我覺得個畫面會同二百萬人一樣咁好睇</span></span></strong></span><br />\n最好有法律巴絲入黎分析下<br />\n一齊入黎討論下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0c2c8f86c1b27357a22e5a473b81e7ab0568530e","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"推到九點"},{"pid":"d6152ceea45a42472c64ce8ccd12f898dff31baa","tid":1626751,"uid":225102,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"十點呀"},{"pid":"e69f1abee6e807b02581c0f7ebd9f78a9aeefbe9","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"推到九點"},{"pid":"262130754076e5ec40b71d4e62abd90d557527bc","tid":1626751,"uid":230060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"b818b09a2ba2348da3913848c80ab5faf1ae331f","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6152ceea45a42472c64ce8ccd12f898dff31baa","tid":1626751,"uid":225102,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"十點呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"九點叫定儲人，十點唱港歌"},{"pid":"a3005139512a547d6239541a060e601832eb8a70","tid":1626751,"uid":43206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11c789801c8dc393f590513219029c864f4720c3","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"九點叫定儲人，十點唱港歌"},{"pid":"5fc7f0d0a86f5f3b489aadaeb17993fcea0f3371","tid":1626751,"uid":238693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"行動post 都上唔撚到熱門，聽日收得皮啦唉"},{"pid":"68e6f2e15287d588d7260676275e13c9c2f8625e","tid":1626751,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"5b01362e805aad5b03d65a9ae137ca8531d65b2a","tid":1626751,"uid":299673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=